{"tid":958084,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"路透社：iPhone 旗艦機或改由印度生產！","createTime":"2018-12-27T13:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T18:06:34.000Z","uid":26418,"like":259,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"d8e42f1092ec3c4a7bc55157531275dabe696aa0","tid":958084,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:43:21.000Z","msg":"路透引述消息人士的消息，指出蘋果將在 2019 年透過鴻海於印度生產高端 iPhone，當中可能包括 iPhone X 系列。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，蘋果已在印度生產 iPhone 6s ne iPhone SE。貿戰開始後，有指如關稅加至 25%，便會將生產線撤出中國。<br />\n<br />\n據報道指出，將組裝 iPhone 的廠房位於印度泰米爾納德邦，而鴻海已投資 250 億盧布擴建廠房，為當地提供 2 萬 5000 個就業機會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/12/27/iphone-production-in-india/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F12%2F27%2Fiphone-production-in-india%2F&d=wP1V4d3dEokp1rN2RNzFfwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=8169a786\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/12/27/iphone-production-in-india/</a> <a href=\"http://newmobile.life/ios\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewmobile.life%2Fios&d=wP1V4d3dEokp1rN2RNzFfwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7f9babb0\" target=\"_blank\">http://newmobile.life/ios</a>"},{"pid":"500f7cd22ff0e0842eb45a4a51f6d6269cd8a24a","tid":958084,"uid":107364,"like":26,"dislike":176,"score":-150,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee37aa52ffde52d092a9e95a4d54be121832efd2","tid":958084,"uid":53676,"like":182,"dislike":2,"score":180,"quote":{"pid":"500f7cd22ff0e0842eb45a4a51f6d6269cd8a24a","tid":958084,"uid":107364,"like":26,"dislike":176,"score":-150,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3833ba16aaa2f4f388944cccc46137211d211676","tid":958084,"uid