%2F12%2F27%2Fiphone-production-in-india%2F&d=wP1V4d3dEokp1rN2RNzFfwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=8169a786\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/12/27/iphone-production-in-india/</a> <a href=\"http://newmobile.life/ios\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewmobile.life%2Fios&d=wP1V4d3dEokp1rN2RNzFfwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7f9babb0\" target=\"_blank\">http://newmobile.life/ios</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T17:50:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你即將進入內容農場：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.newmobilelife.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com&d=wP1V4d3dEokp1rN2RNzFfwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=d5e4228b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.newmobilelife.com</a><br />\n要繼續嗎？若是感到厭煩，放棄也是一種選擇啊。</span>"},{"pid":"1e4af0979fb752678e1067e278d63d39a95045c4","tid":958084,"uid":88029,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T17:51:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"382863c7588c5a83255b9c996c4ed8ed6d67254c","tid":958084,"uid":34140,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T17:53:42.000Z","msg":"班印度垃圾做錯野淨係識得賴，qc真係祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef77206f78ddd1159bf6ec4540c8457f823c744","tid":958084,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"aa69d0b8f78dc76cae352f41c085db53d449bec6","tid":958084,"uid":88029,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"7b6f1e04637c9145cd864e331c549bba51b0854e","tid":958084,"uid":107364,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"44558f58ae6d709da505284dd003d0efd39706bb","tid":958084,"uid":88029,"like":35,"dislike":5,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T15:17:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T17:40:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T17:57:17.000Z","msg":"中國有民主只係時間既問題<img src=\"/assets/face